      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>378</span> - <span>Fuller Form of Personal Name</span> (NR)
      </h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Authority - full</div>
      <div class="datename">September 2011</div>
      <hr />
